; str_to_float path) into a boxed f64 and type 7 (TrivFloat64). node_value returns
; fk_nval unchanged; int_to_str (tag 32) renders the sentinel as true/false and the
; boxed float as text — so the shared json codec emits them right. This lifts the
; float-NodeID node/substrate wall for the json/whisper bands.
